# Food Price Tracker ðŸ›’

A simple Python command-line application for tracking daily prices of food and household items.

## Features

- Add item prices with categories
- Automatic price comparison with previous entries
- Category-based reports (average, highest, lowest)
- Optional date range filtering
- Data stored locally in CSV format

## Categories

- Grains
- Food
- Household
- Drinks
- Other

## Technologies Used

- Python
- CSV file storage
- Git & GitHub

## Why this project?

This project was built to practice real-world Python skills such as:

- Input validation
- File handling
- Data analysis
- Clean function-based design

## How to Run

```bash
python main.py
```
